The 34-year-old actor got engaged to model girlfriend of two years Renee Puente on June 27, 2013, a source revealed to Us Weekly. Morrison's pals Elton John and his husband David Furnish were the ones to blow the lid on the exciting news, announcing it during John's White Tie and Tiara Ball to benefit his AIDS Foundation in London, an insider told the mag. "I'm very happy. Renee's not in the industry -- I need that normality," Morrison told Closer magazine of their relationship. "We like to stay home and cook. We're not that Hollywood."
